       "Damn! They escaped!" Ominous hissed into the Energonian communication 
band. And all they had to show for thier efforst was a busted left naucel and 
several scrapes on the underside of the shuttle. "Return to base."

       Hell Beast found Craken. He was an enourmous bot, and was easy to pick 
on the scanners. A new addition like this was always a welcoming sight.
